    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding a Samurai Weapon</p><hr /><p>The presence of your weapon brings weight to your arguments. As long as your weapon is able to be seen but not drawn, you gain a circumstance bonus to your Diplomacy checks. When your weapon is drawn, the circumstance bonus applies to your Intimidation checks. The bonus is equal to +1 if you are at least trained in the weapon you wield, or +2 if you're a master with it.</p><p>The reaction of an NPC that has already fought you may be different, at the GM's discretion.</p>",
